  "texts": [
    "The industrial chatbot is more user-friendly for operators than HMIs or SCADAs thanks to the natural language format for queries/responses, which impersonates human communications.",
    "To further meet I5.0 basic standards, we integrate two parameters as interlocks for production run: the maximum overtime working hours for employees and the maximum factory pollution rate.",
    "Our industrial chatbot closely tracks these parameters alongside the overall production for operators' sanity and ecosystem preservation.",
    "This research contributes to repositioning humans and their well-being at the center of the production system.",
    "For more flexibility, we design an online and offline chatbot model."
  ],
